reviewText: I have not yet had a chance to view these; but I'm sure I won't be disappointed.  (who would be when they were such a bargain?)

Came damaged.  But I called and it was replaced right away.  New dvd in perfect condition.  Looking forward to watching these movies.

Sound quality on this is horrible... I expected better and for it not to sound like I was watching the movie in a tunnel.  Also, the sub-titles do not work and there are no extra features on the DVD. I expected the movies thenselves to be in just like they would be on a regular dvd and that since there was less packaging they were able to sell them at this price... I mean you get the idea of the movie but it was still less that great.  I won't buy another of these 3 movies in one deals...
BOUGHT IT FOR DISORGANIZED CRIME. CRAZY MOVIE WITH A LOT OF BIG NAMES. THE OTHER TWO ARE GOOD TOO.

Got this for Disorganized Crime.  Love it!  Such a treat to get to see it again and add it to our DVD Library.  This is another movie that we watch regularly.  The other two movies included are a bonus.
It was all i expected it to be

Humorous but plot for each of these movies drags along, when compared to more recent comedy movies by these cast members.  Very talented cast.

I really only wanted Disorganized Crime, and thought I'd get this 3-pack. Disorganized Crime is just as funny as it was when my kids and I watched it years ago.  I enjoyed Money for Nothing and haven't watched Another Stakeout, yet.

I got this  for the movie "Another Stakeout." I watched the other movies Money for Nothing and Disorganized Crime and didn't find them good at all. Another Stakeout was as funny as the first movie and Rosie was great in it. I was laughing from beginning to end in it.

The actors performances were the best,
 3 great movies included in the package, also cuts down on the multiple case storage

I love this movie combination, it has two of my favorite funny movies in it and it was sold at a really cheap price. I can easily watch Disorganized Crime over and over again without growing tired of it, and Another Steakout always makes me laugh, plus it has Dennis Farina in it whom is one of my all time favorite actors. Good bang for your buck. I'd also recommend the seller. The DVD came in good condition as promised, and arrived prior to the fulfillment date. Major plus in my book.
